text:
Look~♡ It's a cute croffle~
from the shop we went to yesterday~

Yeah~ The dough is crispy and fluffy~,
and the cream on top is really sweet~

It was so delicious,
it tasted like happiness~♡

Haha, it makes me feel like I'm eating it too.
Hinana, you're good at taking these kinds of photos.

You always upload them to Twesta and stuff too.
Did you upload this one too?

Not right away~.
If Hinana is still at the shop~.

Many people might come then, right?
So, I upload them after coming back~.

I see... As expected,
Hinana is quite thoughtful.
